---
title: Vegetarian Chili Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: Our chef-curated “perfect plates” are the answer to any dinner woes! Set out a hearty pot of Mexican-spiced vegetarian chili packed with peppers, onions, and tomatoes. Now, bring the fun—a toppings bar complete with fluffy rice, crunchy chips, cheese, sour cream, and scallions! If you ordered extras, make a meaty chili instead or add bacon to the mix!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d7efbd18d6e477003fc8f9-8cad1b79.jpeg
